MachPyomo.ha_pasture_crop_paddocks(model, f, l)¶
Pyomo function.

Total hectares that can be grazed on crop paddocks before seeding *note poc is only on crop paddocks but the seeding activity includes pastures, to stop pasture paddocks providing poc only loop through the crop set
